cast.overview: A Pennsylvania band scores a hit in 1964 and rides the star-making machinery as long as it can, with lots of help from its manager.
cast.title: That Thing You Do!

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Brittney Powell (born on March 4, 1972 in Würzburg, West Germany) is a German-American actress. She also has been credited using the name Brittney Rache. She made several appearances in Playboy during the early 1990s, again as Brittney Rache.
